headline: Parks Associates: 41% of Apartment Renters Expect Their Internet Service Will Be Ready-to-Go at Move-In
summary: Parks Associates today announced the new white paper Achieving Turnkey Connectivity: Elevating the Total Multifamily Experience, in partnership with Xfinity Communities, with research showing that 41% of apartment renters expect their internet service will be ready-to-go from the moment they move into a property.
